00:10:15.970 --> 00:10:17.040
Stark...

00:10:18.140 --> 00:10:18.880
Ne?!

00:10:22.350 --> 00:10:23.640
Bushogoma!

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:32.360
Lilinette!

00:10:32.950 --> 00:10:34.560
Hey, Lilinette!

00:10:37.610 --> 00:10:38.530
Lilinette...

00:10:49.180 --> 00:10:51.710
